All Classes

Class Description
Controller
The Controller class handles EventHandlers and contains the main and start methods.
DrawGardenPane
The DrawGardenPane class contains all JavaFx View elements for the Garden Area of the View.
EncyclopediaPane
The EncyclopediaPane class contains all View elements for the EncylopediaPane.
Model
The Model class contains all data.
Plant
The Plant class contains all plant data.
PlantSearchPane
The PlantSearchPane contains the view for the PlantSearchPane portion of the view.
SavedData
The SavedData Class holds information on the state of save gardens.
Season
The Season Enum contains all season options.
StartPageView
The StartPageView contains all View elements for the Splash Screen.
ToolBarPane
The ToolBarPane class contains all view elements for the ToolBarPane.
View
The View classes contains all pane elements and is the UI of the application Contains all panes.
